1
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:02,120
What are you going to do?

2
00:01:02,120 --> 00:01:03,560
If you want revenge,

3
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:06,840
at least learn to protect yourself first.

4
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:10,920
It's getting late.

5
00:01:11,520 --> 00:01:13,080
Get some rest early.

6
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:35,440
Break the earth.

7
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:42,320
The body is like withered wood.

8
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:45,360
Its steps are like rivers.

9
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:00,400
Open the coffin under an umbrella.

10
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,320
Master, both are empty.

11
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:43,880
Th-What's going on?

12
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:46,160
Where are my son's and that woman's remains?

13
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:49,480
The remains, where did they go?

14
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,720
The coffin shows signs of being pried open.

15
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,560
The remains were stolen.

16
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:58,120
Someone likely doesn't want the resentment to fade.

17
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,320
Protect Master! Protect Master!

18
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:13,000
Help! Help! Help!

19
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:21,880
Th-There's been another murder!

20
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:23,320
Another murder!

21
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,240
Another murder!

22
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:27,280
Master, this way, this way!

23
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:28,280
Let's go.

24
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,680
No weapon, no footprints.

25
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,760
The branch was cut clean through.

26
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,600
Found it, found it.

27
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:54,040
I found that girl's records.

28
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:56,560
I'm really about to faint from hunger.

29
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:58,680
What are you going to reward me with?

30
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:00,000
Roast chicken.

31
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:01,960
Roast chicken.

32
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,600
Talk first.

33
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:07,440
Fine. The girl in the pocket watch is Wang Yueya.

34
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:09,880
She is the daughter of Wang Sanming and Shuang'er.

35
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,840
Because her mother was a prostitute,

36
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:13,600
she was looked down on since childhood.

37
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,520
And the Wangs often abused her.

38
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:18,080
Later, didn't Shuang'er lose her right hand bone?

39
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:20,840
Wang Shengchang used Wang Yueya's right hand bone instead.

40
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:31,000
What are you thinking about?

41
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,040
Hurry up and eat.

42
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,280
Let me wipe that for you.

43
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:41,800
What are you laughing at?

44
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,440
Full now, are you?

45
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:42,920
If you're full, I'll take it away.

46
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:43,920
No, no, no.

47
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,120
I barely ate anything.

48
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:45,920
Just stay there.

49
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:48,920
Where did this eerie wind come from?

50
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:01,920
I know the truth now.

51
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,040
Did you really see a ghost?

52
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,200
I did.

53
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,720
But it wasn't really a vengeful spirit taking lives.

54
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,600
Someone was just playing tricks with ghosts.

55
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:15,760
The victim was pulled halfway into the air by a force.

56
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:19,720
Then dragged through the air for some distance.

57
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,960
In the end, the arm was severed.

58
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:23,680
And the victim bled to death.

59
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:26,080
But didn't you say no person has that kind of strength?

60
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,280
A person can't.

61
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:29,280
But the wind can.

62
00:05:36,280 --> 00:05:37,960
This so-called ghost woman killing

63
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:40,360
was actually a giant kite.

64
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,960
This season often brings strong winds.

65
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:45,840
And the force produced by such a huge kite

66
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,440
is enough to lift an adult into the sky.

67
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,920
But the victim's wound was so clean.

68
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,320
How exactly was it done?

69
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,160
No murder weapon was found at the scene.

70
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:05,680
What if the kite string was made of special sharp wire?

71
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:14,960
The Wang family's lanterns were mysteriously cut down.

72
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:16,280
They fell to the ground.

73
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:20,560
And the branches in the Wang graveyard were cut too.

74
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:24,480
All of this was caused by the kite.

75
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:28,040
The killer hung white cloth behind the kite.

76
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:30,480
One side of the cloth was rigged with fine wire in advance.

77
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,760
When the target approached the white cloth,

78
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:35,440
the rising kite would lift the cloth with it.

79
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,280
And wrap it around the target.

80
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:41,320
Hidden in the dark, the killer worked it like a puppet.

81
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:44,360
Making the fine wire coil around the victim's right arm.

82
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,960
Then using the wind's force to cut the arm off.

83
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:53,120
The lantern cords and branches were cut by that wire too.

84
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:57,600
That murder method is truly ingenious.

85
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:02,040
Then what was the killer's motive?

86
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,680
Just as you found in your investigation,

87
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:08,400
Shuang'er and her daughter suffered every humiliation in the Wang house.

88
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:09,600
And the dead man

89
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:12,240
was very likely one of those who abused them.

90
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,720
Before this, Xu Nan and I

91
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,920
I happened into Shuang'er's room from before she died

92
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:20,120
The room had been sealed for three years

93
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:22,600
But there were signs of worship there

94
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:26,480
It shows someone was secretly burning joss paper for them

95
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:30,200
The killer used the severed hand case for revenge

96
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:33,520
Because that mother and daughter also lacked a right hand

97
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:39,120
Then who is the killer?

98
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,760
Someone who could, in the Wang family's garden and graveyard,

99
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:43,680
set up such a carefully laid trap

100
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:46,720
must meet two conditions

101
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:47,960
First

102
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:49,760
be extremely familiar with the place

103
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:52,560
Second, be able to come and go freely

104
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:55,400
And the one who could meet both conditions

105
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:57,440
could only be a servant of the Wang family

106
00:07:58,320 --> 00:08:00,080
That day, in Shuang'er's room

107
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:02,240
I also caught a special smell

108
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,520
It was Guandong tobacco

109
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:05,000
It is rather expensive

110
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,760
In the Wang family, the one who can afford this tobacco

111
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,640
is only that person
